Cell["\<\
The HilbertBalance.wl file should be placed in the same directory as this \
file. Before proceeding, ensure that Normaliz \
(https://www.normaliz.uni-osnabrueck.de/) is installed and specify the full \
path of normaliz.exe (note that for Linux and Mac users, the filename may \
differ). And run the following line to import HilbertBalance\
\>", "Subsubsection",
